---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.webp';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About the Architecture"
	description="How this AI Efficiency Hub is built and why it exists."
	pubDate={new Date('January 01 2026')}
	heroImage="/assets/post-scarcity-cover.webp"
>
	<div class="mission-statement">
		<p class="lead">
			Content is no longer limited by human speed. Quality is no longer limited by human fatigue. 
			<strong>This entire website is a testament to that fact.</strong>
		</p>
	</div>

	<h3>The "Super Individual" Philosophy</h3>
	<p>
		We believe that in the age of AI, a single developer can wield the output of a 10-person agency. 
		The <strong>AI Efficiency Hub</strong> is built to prove this concept. It is not just a blog; it is an 
		<em>autonomous asset</em> managed by AI Agents, curated by human vision.
	</p>

    <div class="agent-workforce">
        <h3>Meet the Workforce</h3>
        <p class="section-desc">The specialized agents running this operation 24/7.</p>
        
        <div class="agent-grid">
            <div class="agent-card">
                <h4>Clawdbot</h4>
                <div class="agent-role">System Architect</div>
                <p>Manages deployment pipelines, error logging, and self-healing infrastructure.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="agent-card">
                <h4>Oracle</h4>
                <div class="agent-role">Trend Analyst</div>
                <p>Scans 500+ RSS feeds daily to identify rising AI tools and patterns.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="agent-card">
                <h4>DaVinci</h4>
                <div class="agent-role">Visual Director</div>
                <p>Generates cover art, optimizes SVGs, and maintains design consistency.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="agent-card">
                <h4>Justitia</h4>
                <div class="agent-role">Auditor</div>
                <p>Verifies factuality, checks for bias, and ensures SEO compliance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

	<div class="stats-grid">
		<div class="stat-card">
			<div class="stat-number">100%</div>
			<div class="stat-label">AI-Assisted Operations</div>
		</div>
		<div class="stat-card">
			<div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
			<div class="stat-label">Content Optimization</div>
		</div>
		<div class="stat-card">
			<div class="stat-number">0ms</div>
			<div class="stat-label">Human Bottlenecks</div>
		</div>
	</div>

    <div class="tech-stack-section">
        <h3>Built With</h3>
        <div class="tech-grid">
             <div class="tech-item">Astro 5.0</div>
             <div class="tech-item">Tailwind (Custom)</div>
             <div class="tech-item">Python 3.12</div>
             <div class="tech-item">Vercel Edge</div>
             <div class="tech-item">OpenAI GPT-4o</div>
             <div class="tech-item">Anthropic Claude 3.5</div>
        </div>
    </div>

	<div class="cta-box">
		<h4>Ready to scale your own output?</h4>
		<p>Explore our library of guides and start building your own agent workforce.</p>
		<a href="/blog" class="btn">Browse the Library</a>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.mission-statement {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		color: #fff;
	}
	.lead strong {
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.stats-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 3rem 0;
	}
	.stat-card {
		background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
		backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
		border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.stat-number {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		background: linear-gradient(to right, #6FB1FC, #ACE0F9);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.stat-label {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--gray);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}
	.cta-box {
		margin-top: 4rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(35, 213, 171, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));
		border: 1px solid rgba(35, 213, 171, 0.2);
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 24px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.cta-box h4 {
		margin-top: 0;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
	}
	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--accent);
		color: #000;
		padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 100px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		transition: transform 0.2s;
	}
	.btn:hover {
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}
	/* ... existing styles ... */
    
    .section-desc {
        color: var(--gray);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    /* Agent Grid */
    .agent-workforce {
        margin: 4rem 0;
    }
    .agent-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .agent-card {
        background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 16px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .agent-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }
    .agent-avatar {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .agent-card h4 {
        margin: 0;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .agent-role {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .agent-card p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--gray);
    }

    /* Tech Stack */
    .tech-stack-section {
        margin: 4rem 0;
    }
    .tech-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.8rem;
    }
    .tech-item {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #e2e8f0;
        font-family: monospace;
    }

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.stats-grid { 
            grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        .agent-grid { 
            grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
        }
        .mission-statement {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding-left: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .cta-box {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        .cta-box h4 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
	}
</style>
